{"tid":1710363,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(突發)奶共01公投 你認為西灣河警員開真槍是否合理？","createTime":"2019-11-12T07:14:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T08:41:30.000Z","uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0a18def9893077d07ae0232adf5d75154b3fe1d1","tid":1710363,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:14:12.000Z","msg":"西灣河今早有警員使用實彈連開三槍，至少一名青年中槍倒地。同時有傳沙田、大圍、旺角等地均有警員舉槍指向市民及人群。縱使警方於今年10月初承認曾對「武力與槍械的使用」作出修改，你認為在現今情況使用實彈是否合理？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edigest.hk/article/123704/%e7%86%b1%e8%a9%b1/%e6%8a%95%e7%a5%a8-%e4%bd%a0%e8%aa%8d%e7%82%ba-%e8%a5%bf%e7%81%a3%e6%b2%b3-%e8%ad%a6%e5%93%a1%e9%96%8b%e6%a7%8d-%e6%98%af%e5%90%a6%e5%90%88%e7%90%86/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2Farticle%2F123704%2F%25e7%2586%25b1%25e8%25a9%25b1%2F%25e6%258a%2595%25e7%25a5%25a8-%25e4%25bd%25a0%25e8%25aa%258d%25e7%2582%25ba-%25e8%25a5%25bf%25e7%2581%25a3%25e6%25b2%25b3-%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%2593%25a1%25e9%2596%258b%25e6%25a7%258d-%25e6%2598%25af%25e5%2590%25a6%25e5%2590%2588%25e7%2590%2586%2F&d=UyoO8KdNfTPb55o7yEEco2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=0a3f37d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edigest.hk/article/123704/%e7%86%b1%e8%a9%b1/%e6%8a%95%e7%a5%a8-%e4%bd%a0%e8%aa%8d%e7%82%ba-%e8%a5%bf%e7%81%a3%e6%b2%b3-%e8%ad%a6%e5%93%a1%e9%96%8b%e6%a7%8d-%e6%98%af%e5%90%a6%e5%90%88%e7%90%86/</a><br />\n<br />\n現時係<span style=\"color: red;\">96%</span>不需開槍 VS <span style=\"color: red;\">4%</span>應該開槍<br />\n可惜呀叻唔會信奶共01啦"},{"pid":"72e0b1d15feff5e6eb734f5a63a40701e0a8f6e2","tid":1710363,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:15:13.000Z","msg":"罷睇01<br />\n<br />\n［全民罷工妙計］繁忙時間要引狗衝入港鐵站向返工人士施襲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1708303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1708303</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f07558e0cf06558a610810bbeb77a3045219f531","tid":1710363,"uid":160247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2